import { combineReducers } from 'redux'
import authedReducer from './authedReducer.js'
import userReducer from './userReducer.js'
import constituencyReducer from './constituencyReducer.js'
import voteReducer from './voteReducer.js'
import electionReducer from './electionReducer.js'
import constituencyCandidateReducer from './constituencyCandidateReducer.js'
import loadingReducer from './loadingReducer.js'
import electionResultReducer from './electionResultReducer.js'


export default combineReducers({
    authedUser: authedReducer,
    users: userReducer,
    constituencies: constituencyReducer,
    vote: voteReducer,
    election: electionReducer,
    constituencyCandidates: constituencyCandidateReducer,
    loading: loadingReducer,
    electionResult: electionResultReducer
})
